{"tid":1755651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"塞路軌幫大家戒黨鐵？？","createTime":"2019-11-25T16:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T16:34:33.000Z","uid":288753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6bcba8fc9794ab7fa72e9c1fac4a1d79aff1cf71","tid":1755651,"uid":288753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:34:09.000Z","msg":"即係點？塞唔塞路軌？要香港停工，是一定沒可能。<br />\n<br />\n但我地提倡抵制黨鐵，白白咁降低人流，去比班藍絲上班上得舒服Ｄ？定係已經見區選贏，就已經好多野都堅持唔到落去，已經又因為方便，又要用番黨鐵？塞鐵拆鐵，不塞路，幫大家停用黨鐵。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eMKUbNj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeMKUbNj.jpg&h=6d10767a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cbe4691e1ce1f57cd1e52e567ff9dfdeb0060a1c","tid":1755651,"uid":36808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:34:33.000Z","msg":"唔好意思 阻一阻大家時間<br />\n<br />\n希望手足可以幫下家長車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無言感激<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1747239\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1747239</a>"}]}